An interesting species apparently not rare in the higher mountains of Hispaniola. The specimens cited above agree “ exactly with each other and with the type 01 Proustia do- minqensis SPR. in the Prodromus Herbarium. The type specimen 01 Lepidaploa bumisolz'a CASS. has not been seen. The good description 01 CASSINI agrees perfectly with the species as here understood.
